    SELECT b.id, b."createdDate", b."fileName", b."pageFileid", b.path, b.storage, b.title, b."updatedDate"
    FROM "bannerFiles" AS b
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
INNER JOIN "pageFiles" AS p ON t."pageFileid" = p.id

FROM (
    SELECT b.id, b."createdDate", b."fileName", b."pageFileid", b.path, b.storage, b.title, b."updatedDate"
    FROM "bannerFiles" AS b
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
INNER JOIN "pageFiles" AS p ON t."pageFileid" = p.id

    SELECT b.id, b."createdDate", b."fileName", b."pageFileid", b.path, b.storage, b.title, b."updatedDate"
    FROM "bannerFiles" AS b
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
INNER JOIN "pageFiles" AS p ON t."pageFileid" = p.id
